data.description: ***OFFERING $15,000.00 TOWARD CLOSING COSTS.*** Welcome to your future home in Providence, Davenport! This spacious 5-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom house is all about comfort and style for your family. The modern kitchen with granite countertops and stainless-steel appliances is a dream for cooking enthusiasts. Open the sliding doors and unveil a covered patio and a generous backyard.    Upstairs, you'll find a roomy loft and a luxurious master suite with two walk-in closets and a spa-like bathroom. But there's more to it. Providence is an exceptional community with a top-notch clubhouse, pools, tennis courts, and an 18-hole golf course.    Enjoy a prime location with access to exciting attractions like Disney World and Universal Studios. Plus, you'll be close to shops, restaurants, and much more. Don't miss this unique opportunity. Call now and schedule a visit to make this house your home in the incredible Providence community! Moreover, with no Community Development District (not CDD) fees and a low Homeowners Association (HOA) payment, playing golf here isn't a luxury—it's a lifestyle!    Owning a house with all these amenities and a prime location can offer stability and long-term investment benefits compared to renting. It's a great opportunity to consider buying if it fits your long-term plans. If you have any questions or need more information, feel free to ask!
